    <contentText>
      <Value><![CDATA[Umbraco AI is a built-in assistant that helps you work faster and smarter inside the Umbraco backoffice. Whether you are a developer building a new site or an editor managing daily content, Umbraco AI is designed to make your work easier.

You can use Umbraco AI to write and improve content directly on any page. Ask it to draft a blog post, rewrite a description, or suggest a headline. It understands your content and responds in plain, clear language.

Umbraco AI also helps with tasks beyond writing. You can ask it to search for media, update properties, or fetch information from external sources. It works alongside you in the backoffice, so you do not need to switch between tools or tabs.

The assistant follows your brand guidelines automatically. This means the content it produces matches your tone, audience, and style without you having to give detailed instructions every time.

Getting started is straightforward. Open any document in the content section and look for the AI assistant panel. Type your request in plain language and the assistant will respond with suggestions or take action on your behalf.

Umbraco AI is built with content editors in mind. It removes repetitive tasks, reduces the time spent on first drafts, and helps you maintain consistency across your site. The more you use it, the more useful it becomes.

If you manage a large site with many pages, Umbraco AI can help you keep content fresh and on-brand. It is a practical tool that fits naturally into your existing workflow, without requiring any technical knowledge to use.]]></Value>
    </contentText>
